<p class="MsoNormal"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: normal;"><em><a id="irc_mil" style="border: 0px currentColor;" href="http://www.google.co.uk/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;frm=1&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;docid=6LF7qIC8vpKsNM&amp;tbnid=uMcW5dHTlXPrgM:&amp;ved=0CAUQjRw&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.holidayapartmentpoland.com%2Fgreatescape.htm&amp;ei=KbxGUq7MOoKLtAaJh4CQAw&amp;bvm=bv.53217764,d.Yms&amp;psig=AFQjCNFZt0YZ-1flKA7DMn9aEu7nEh4Itw&amp;ust=1380453783510360" data-ved="0CAUQjRw"><img id="irc_mi" style="margin-top: 77px;" src="http://www.holidayapartmentpoland.com/greatescape.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="406" /></a></em></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><em><strong>FILM SOCIETY - The stuff that dreams are made of!</strong></em></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold; display: inline !important;">Do you consider yourself a movie buff? Do you spend so much time at the cinema that the entire staff (including the cleaners) know your name and life story? Are you vaguely aware that nowadays we have moving pictures that convey a story to you over the space of about...90 -120 minutes? If so, FILM SOC is the society for you!</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold;">Every Wednesday evening we storm the JCR and throw on a film. It could be a classic, it could be a box office hit, it could be arthouse. It could also be something totally random that a member's brought along simply because they feel it's the kind of film that requires total societal appreciation.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold;">Every so often we also do cinema trips to either Durham or Newcastle (last year we went to see Burke and Hare, Thor, Despicable Me and Black Swan) which also serves as an extra opportunity to hang out with the awesomeness that is the society.</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold;">Oh and the banter - we banter like pros.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em><em>That's all from me I think! Hopefully I will see you all at the Fresher's fair. Otherwise, you can email me for more details and to be added to the mailing list.</em></em></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-weight: bold;">- El Presidente</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a id="irc_mil" style="border: 0px currentColor;" href="http://www.google.co.uk/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;frm=1&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;docid=6LF7qIC8vpKsNM&amp;tbnid=uMcW5dHTlXPrgM:&amp;ved=0CAUQjRw&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.holidayapartmentpoland.com%2Fgreatescape.htm&amp;ei=KbxGUq7MOoKLtAaJh4CQAw&amp;bvm=bv.53217764,d.Yms&amp;psig=AFQjCNFZt0YZ-1flKA7DMn9aEu7nEh4Itw&amp;ust=1380453783510360" data-ved="0CAUQjRw"></a>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>